# Prompt: Implement Complete JSON Tools Suite for phung.work
## Objective
Expand the existing JSON tools into a complete, professional JSON toolkit comparable to JSONLint, CodeBeautify, FreeFormatter, and DevUtils.
The implementation must follow the existing architecture and UI of **phung.work**.
## Core Principles
* Everything runs entirely in the browser.
* No backend.
* No API calls.
* No user data leaves the browser.
* Fast and lightweight.
* Support files up to 20MB.
* Mobile responsive.
* Dark mode compatible.
* Accessible (WCAG AA).
* Modular architecture.
* Reuse existing shared components.
* Do not modify existing routing or application flow unless absolutely necessary.
